            <h1 class="cw-h1">IxTheo Innovative</h1>
            <p>In addition to books and journals, other information sources which go beyond the contents of a traditional bibliography are searchable in the Index Theologicus (IxTheo). Thus, you can pursue specific research questions but also discover new media.</p>
            <p>After any search, you can use the “Format” facet on the right-hand side next to the list of results to select certain types of publications or sources in your search results. There are also several innovative tools to facilitate the searching process.</p>

