                            <div class="collapse" id="collapse-inno-1">
                                <div class="card card-body">
                                    <p>Many researchers and institutions publish content in blogs and podcasts. Some comment primarily on current events in the church and in theology; others deal in longer series and more in depth with topics in theology and religious studies. Many of these contributions aim to present current research in a manner accessible to the greater public.</p>
                                    <p>You can search for relevant blogs by selecting the option “Weblog” in the “Format” facet in IxTheo.</p>
                                    <p>It is also possible to follow several blogs and podcasts at the same time by using IxTheo’s feed aggregator. Once you’ve selected the blogs and podcasts you wish to follow, you are informed per e-mail or RSS-feed whenever a new contribution or episode is available.</p>
                                    <p>You can get an overview of all blogs currently accessible through IxTheo with <a href="<?=$this->url('search-results', [], ['query' => ['lookfor' => '','type'=>'AllFields','filter' => 'format:"Weblog"']]); ?>">this search query</a>.</p>
